<p>*Student academic societies are not primarily organized for recreational activities, parties, community service, or student support and well being. These may be an incidental part of what a student academic society might do, but not their primary focus. Student organizations whose primary purpose is recreational, social, or community service should be organized under the auspices of the BYU-Idaho Activities Program. Student organizations whose primary purpose is student well-being and support should be organized under the auspices of the BYU-Idaho Dean of Students.</p>]]></IntroCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="CellGroup" label="Cells" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true" ID="5"><numColumns type="enumeration" values="1 2 3 4 5" label="Select number of cell columns." readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true" ID="6">2</numColumns><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Cell" Name="CellList" label="Cell List" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="true" ID="7"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Cell" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="CellComponent" Expanded="false" ID="8"/></xPower></xPower><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_BannerAd" Name="BannerAds" label="Rotating Ads (650x216px required)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="true" ID="9"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="BannerAd" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false" ID="10"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="BannerAd" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="BannerAdComponent" Expanded="false" ID="10"/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="" Query="" Name="DeptEvents" label="Define Your Events Folder" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded